== NEO4IC ==
[[File:Neo4ic promo.webp|thumb|Official promotion for VRChat x NEO4IC "Tree of Realms" collaboration shirt for New Years Eve 2023.]]
NEO4IC (pronounced ''"neo-phoric"'') is a company that creates techwear clothing and accessories. For the [[Special:MyLanguage/New Years Eve|New Years Eve]] 2023 event, VRChat partnered with NEO4IC to release a collaboration t-shirt<ref>[https://neo4ic.com/products/vrchat-tree-of-realms VRChat Tree of Realms] on ''neo4ic.com''; retrieved December 7, 2024.</ref>, dubbed the "Tree of Realms". NEO4IC was given a collaboration booth inside the New Years Eve 2023 event world.